"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T00:47:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/26/084729_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F26%2F084729_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=86dcaf98&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T00:51:26.000Z","msg":"收皮啦隱藏性五毛關愛座， 睇見你條五毛 屌飯民 仲落力個屌建制派就笑撚左， 仲要買中資股 做中資股大股東， 口裏說反中國， 心裏卻很誠實"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T01:18:10.000Z","msg":"以為改咗名唔認得你呀五毛狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T01:39:34.000Z","msg":"真係笑大人個口， 根本方國珊就係最好嗰個， 佢就係民主派， 點似得你隻 五毛 屌泛民 仲 屌得落力個建制派<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ， 仲要買中資股<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ， 根本連登仔最鍾意就係方國珊， 點會好似你隻五毛咁叫人投白票 乘機 幫助建制派<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d17688ede12927f77bfd158b81460d0b5e34060","tid":605374,"uid":38523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T01:41:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/593908/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/593908/page/1</a><br />\n關狗扮捉五毛就大家都知<br />\n補選時一直屌泛民 放生保皇狗比人踢爆<br />\n一直轉移視線<br />\n之後反對佢既人就會有一堆五毛和應<br />\n之後就會順勢比關狗一齊打<br />\n結果就係反保皇狗既巴打就比佢話係五毛<br />\n今日關狗諗住開分身點知唔記得轉ac<br />\n<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/593631/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/593631/page/1</a><br />\n雖然佢又話自嘲又成<br />\n係唔係想用分身開真係一睇就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但..一個恐怖既假設就出現<br />\n如果<br />\n果堆著名五毛原來就係佢既分身呢?<br />\n借住打五毛獲得信任<br />\n係補選時用呢點暗助保皇狗<br />\n一有人反保皇狗<br />\n佢就開埋分身去支持<br />\n再用佢關狗打五毛既身份連同反保皇狗既巴打一齊打呢?<br />\n要知道就算佢打一千一萬個五毛<br />\n都唔及影響一個議席來得緊要<br />\n係咪就解得通佢一直口講泛民保皇一樣<br />\n但一直只追屌泛民放生保皇<br />\n大家可以諗諗"},{"pid":"434aa80d5a042ab4163c50188500831afd384c6d","tid":605374,"uid":38523,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ca5f2ec04594386931953e4d4fcf4d06469b56de","tid":605374,"uid":99568,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"792ac6b0d3e02e5c13d0cc2e129032fff9e61b82","tid":605374,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"1d504d6c073cad94c863b0a7c83b68eed3680715","tid":605374,"uid":99568,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T00:51:26.000Z","msg":"收皮啦隱藏性五毛關愛座， 睇見你條五毛 屌飯民 仲落力個屌建制派就笑撚左， 仲要買中資股 做中資股大股東， 口裏說反中國， 心裏卻很誠實"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T01:18:10.000Z","msg":"以為改咗名唔認得你呀五毛狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T01:39:34.000Z","msg":"真係笑大人個口， 根本方國珊就係最好嗰個， 佢就係民主派， 點似得你隻 五毛 屌泛民 仲 屌得落力個建制派<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ， 仲要買中資股<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ， 根本連登仔最鍾意就係方國珊， 點會好似你隻五毛咁叫人投白票 乘機 幫助建制派<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T01:43:06.000Z","msg":"根本佢就係保皇狗打手<br />\n已經好明顯<br />\n我專登開個post屌保皇狗<br />\n佢入來第一句就係用泛民轉移視線<br />\n佢依加比我踢爆<br />\n已經冇得駁<br />\n不停開垃圾post以量去洗"},{"pid":"8e198d9a9c852094455fc915b0e5932ea25150c7","tid":605374,"uid":1159,"like":1,"dislike":